    <div class="container"> 
     <div id="story-grid" class="row"> 
      <div class="col-md-5 col-md-offset-1" id="engineering-technology"> 
       <div class="row"> 
        <div class="col-md-12"> 
         <h2><i class="fa fa-lightbulb-o" style="color: #EAAB00;"></i> Engineering and technology</h2> 
         <p class="margin-bottom-20"><em>Stanford faculty and students are conducting research to make the Internet more secure.</em></p> 
         <ul class="headline-list"> 
          <li><a href="http://engineering.stanford.edu/news/stanford-computer-scientists-extend-web-browsers-make-internet-safer">Stanford computer scientists extend Web browsers to make the Internet safer</a></li> 
          <li> <a href="http://news.stanford.edu/news/2014/january/business-spying-dangers-011614.html">Surveillance threatens U.S. business climate, democracy, say Stanford researchers</a> </li> 
          <li><a href="http://news.stanford.edu/news/2014/march/nsa-phone-surveillance-031214.html">Stanford students show that phone record surveillance can yield vast amounts of information</a></li> 
          <li><a href="https://engineering.stanford.edu/news/engineering-student-combines-legal-computing-acumen-make-big-public-impact">Engineering student combines legal and computing acumen to make a big public impact</a></li> 
         </ul> 
        </div> 
       </div> 
      </div> 
      <div class="col-md-5 spacing" id="policy-law"> 
       <div class="row"> 
        <div class="col-md-12"> 
         <h2><i class="fa fa-shield" style="color: #0098DB;"></i> Policy and law</h2> 
         <p class="margin-bottom-20"><em>Stanford takes an interdisciplinary approach to such issues as the balance between national security and privacy.</em></p> 
        </div> 
       </div> 
       <div class="row"> 
        <ul class="headline-list"> 
         <li><a href="http://cyberlaw.stanford.edu/">The Center for Internet and Society at Stanford is a leader in the study of the law and policy around emerging technologies</a></li> 
         <li><a href="http://cisac.fsi.stanford.edu/news/takeaway-inaugural-cyber-boot-camp-nothing-secure">Inaugural cyber boot camp brings congressional staffers to Silicon Valley</a></li> 
         <li> <a href="http://news.stanford.edu/news/2014/august/cybersecurity-boot-camp-082614.html">Google's Eric Schmidt tells Stanford gathering that the key to cybersecurity is better encryption</a> </li> 
         <li><a href="http://cisac.fsi.stanford.edu/news/nsa-chief-admiral-michael-rogers-addresses-stanford">NSA director calls for partnership with Silicon Valley to combat cyber attacks</a></li> 
         <li><a href="http://cisac.fsi.stanford.edu/news/media-and-edward-snowden-evening-barton-gellman">Barton Gellman on Edward Snowden and privacy</a></li> 
        </ul> 
       </div> 
      </div> 
